text: Novoalexeyevsky () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Dmitriyevskoye Rural Settlement of Koshekhablsky District, Adygea, Russia. The population was 325 as of 2018. There are 7 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Koshekhablsky District
title: Novoalexeyevsky, Republic of Adygea
